text: Kushkulevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Baygildinsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 62 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 37 km from Krasnaya Gorka, 7 km from Baygildino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Kushkulevo
